name: navigate_up
description: Navigate back to the previous screen or parent view.

name: edit_contact
description: Open the edit mode to modify contact details.

name: add_to_favorites
description: Add the current contact to favorites.

name: open_more_options
description: Open a menu with additional options for the contact.

name: call_contact
description: Initiate a phone call to the selected contact.
parameters: {'contact_number': 'Which phone number do you want to call?'}

name: send_text_message
description: Send a text message to the selected contact.
parameters: {'contact_number': 'Which phone number do you want to text?'}

name: setup_video_call
description: Set up a video call using Duo for the selected contact.

name: open_clock_app
description: Open the Clock app on the device.
